<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='360220' id='t-360220'>and harness the power of digital media</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='362176' id='t-362176'>to do some of this action.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='364687' id='t-364687'>What's happening now with PAWA?</span>
